==Using mongodump
	==backup 
		mongodump --host <hostname> --port <port> -u <username> -p <password> --authenticationDatabase admin --db <database_name> --out /path/to/backup/directory
	==restore
		mongorestore --host <hostname> --port <port> -u <username> -p <password> --authenticationDatabase admin --db <target_db_name> /path/to/backup/directory
==Best Practices
	Schedule regular backups

	Test restore procedures

	Store backups in a different location

	Consider backup retention policies

	For large databases, consider incremental backups
	
